arts.sum: Eddie Nketiah is also expected to return on Saturday after having been out since pre-season with a hamstring injury. Crystal Palace prepare to host bitter rivals Millwall at Selhurst Park on Tuesday for the second time this calendar year.

arts.sum: Crystal Palace prepare to host bitter rivals Millwall at Selhurst Park on Tuesday for the second time this calendar year. In March Palace won 3-1 in the fifth round of the FA Cup with goals coming from Daniel Munoz, Eddie Nketiah, Wes Harding and an own goal from Japhet Tanganga.
